content.p: Issue 01/18 (29) The announcement of winners and prize-giving session was held on 6 December 2017. Chan Zi Yang, a PhD student from the School of Pharmacy, was announced the winner. Meanwhile, Nguyen Nhat Tan, a PhD student from the Nottingham University Business School (NUBS) was announced the recipient of the People's Choice award. The winners share their experience participating and subsequently winning the photography competition. They also share some insights and tips for future participants.
